          "settings": {
            "icon_svg": "",
            "title": "Global Presence",
            "text": "<p>With a strong export network, we cater to clients across multiple international markets. Our focus is on building long-term partnerships by offering reliability, competitive pricing, and premium quality products.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_block_pCtaHp": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "icon_svg": "",
            "title": "Our Vision",
            "text": "<p>To become a trusted global food brand that promotes healthier eating habits, especially for children, by offering natural and nutritious freeze-dried foods. We aim to support a healthier future while staying honest, responsible, and true to our values.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_block_r4FFhj": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "icon_svg": "",
            "title": "Our Mission",
            "text": "<p>To provide safe, high-quality freeze-dried fruits and vegetables that<br>help families choose better snacking options. At a time when childhood obesity<br>is rising due to junk food consumption, we want to offer natural,<br>preservative-free alternatives that are light, nutritious, and convenient. We<br>are committed to ethical practices, food safety, and creating products that<br>truly support children’s health and overall well-being.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
