      "name": "Achievements & Message",
      "settings": {
        "achievements_title": "Achievements",
        "chairman_title": "Chairman’s Message",
        "chairman_message": "<p>At Shubhalaxmi Food Industry, our journey since 1962 has been guided by integrity, quality, and long-term vision. We believe sustainable success comes from trust, ethical practices, and continuous improvement. As we grow globally, our commitment to purity and excellence remains unwavering.</p>",
        "chairman_name": "Sougat Foods",
        "chairman_designation": "Chairman, Sougat Foods",
        "director_title": "Director's Message",
        "director_message": "<p>At Sougat Foods, our commitment goes beyond business — it is about responsibility. We believe food should be safe, honest, and nourishing for every family. In a world where unhealthy eating habits are increasing, especially among children, we strive to offer natural and trustworthy alternatives.</p><p>Through ethical sourcing, strict quality standards, and responsible manufacturing, we ensure that every product reflects our values of integrity, transparency, and care. Our goal is not just to grow as a company, but to contribute positively to society by promoting healthier lifestyles.</p>",
        "director_name": "Ankit Agrawal",
        "director_designation": "Director, Sougat Foods",
